column2: Cowessess First Nation #73 Leadership & their Legal Counsel  No More Delays!
column5: The petition of concerned citizens of the Cowessess First Nation #73 draws to the attention of the elected Leadership of Cowessess First Nation #73 & to the Legal Counsel of individual Cowessess First Nation #73 Councillors that there are serious concerns. Of upmost concern is the interruption of programs & services,,, Please do not allow for further delays of this important Federal Court Case. We want this resolved now!"
